  "body": "Switch the `TestHuggingFaceEndpoint` serverless inference provider from `sambanova` to `together` for `Llama-3.3-70B-Instruct`. Sambanova doesn't support `tool_choice: \"any\"` (needed by `test_structured_few_shot_examples` and `test_unicode_tool_call_integration`) and doesn't return `usage_metadata` in streaming responses.",
